# GiveWP Gateway API


The GiveWP Gateway API is how our application interfaces our donation form with external payment gateways.

The following should be used as reference for the API:
- PaymentGateway framework folder: `src/Framework/PaymentGateways/`
- PaymentGateway abstract class: `src/Framework/PaymentGateways/PaymentGateway.php`
- PaymentGateway interface: `/src/PaymentGateways/PaymentGateway.php`
- PaymentGatewayRegister registrar: `src/Framework/PaymentGateways/PaymentGatewayRegister.php`
- SubscriptionModule abstract class: `src/Framework/PaymentGateways/SubscriptionModule.php`
- Public high level documentation: https://givewp.com/documentation/developers/how-to-build-a-gateway-add-on-for-givewp/

The following should be used as reference on how to implement a gateway using the gateway api:
- TestGateway: `src/PaymentGateways/Gateways/TestGateway/TestGateway.php`
- StripeGateway: `src/PaymentGateways/Gateways/Stripe/StripePaymentElementGateway/StripePaymentElementGateway.php`



